This is test application for ActiveWizards job offer.

----------------------------------------------
What is used:
----------------------------------------------
- Python 2.7.6
- Flask 0.10.1
- PyMongo 2.8

----------------------------------------------
PROJECT STRUCTURE
----------------------------------------------
init-script.sh - uploads data from http://media.mongodb.org/zips.json to local MongoDB storage
run.py - runs the application (using default port 5000)
modules/ - contains buisness logic of application 
modules/templates - contains templates
modules/static - contatins static data

----------------------------------------------
USER GUIDE
----------------------------------------------
Application has two possible URLs mapping:
- http://localhost:5000/get - RESTful method that returns first 20 of the most populated cities as JSON
- http://localhost:5000/chart - displays chart, based on JSON data received from /get. This is a result of application execution

